title: Spain 2 Year Note Yield
description: Spain 2Y Bond Yield was 2.31 percent on Thursday November 3, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the Spain 2 Year Note Yield reached an all time high of 7.13 in July of 2012. This page includes a chart with historical data for Spain 2Y Bond Yield.
